有史以来制作成本最高的电影是哪部？ https://www.nme.com/news/film/what-is-the-most-expense-movie-ever-made-3532938?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=what-is-the-most-expective-movie-做过Will RichardsThu, 09 Nov 2023 00:01:46 +0000 Film NewsNews https://www.nme.com/?p=3532938 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/cinema-screen-audience-film-2000x1270-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="观众在电影院看电影" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/cinema-screen-audience-film-2000x1270-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/cinema-screen-audience-film-2000x1270-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/cinema-screen-audience-film-2000x1270-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/cinema-screen-audience-film-2000x1270-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/cinema-screen-audience-film-2000x1270-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/cinema-screen-audience-film-2000x1270-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>近年来，好莱坞大片花费了一些令人眼花缭乱的资金</p><p>帖子<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/what-is-the-most-expensive-movie-ever-made-3532938">有史以来最昂贵的电影是什么？</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/cinema-screen-audience-film-2000x1270-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="观众在电影院看电影" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/cinema-screen-audience-film-2000x1270-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/cinema-screen-audience-film-2000x1270-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/cinema-screen-audience-film-2000x1270-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/cinema-screen-audience-film-2000x1270-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/cinema-screen-audience-film-2000x1270-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/cinema-screen-audience-film-2000x1270-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>好莱坞大片在全球票房收入数百万（如果幸运的话甚至数十亿），但制作成本也令人难以置信。在这里，我们列出了有史以来最昂贵的电影。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/film-features/best-films-2023-asteroid-city-spider-man-m3gan-keanu-reeves-3464612">2023 年最佳电影……到目前为止！</a></strong></li></ul><p>历史上最昂贵的电影名单不断变化，预算和价格每年都在上涨。</p><p>去年，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/james-cameron">詹姆斯·卡梅隆 (James Cameron)</a>将<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/avatar"><em>《阿凡达：水道》</em></a>的制作成本描述为<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/avatar-the-way-of-water-reveals-very-fucking-expensive-budget-3358219">“非常昂贵”</a> ，他告诉<a href="http://go.redirectingat.com/?id=44681X1458326&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gq.com%2Fstory%2Fjames-cameron-profile-men-of-the-year-2022%3Futm_source%3Dtwitter%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_brand%3Dgq%26mbid%3Dsocial_twitter%26utm_social-type%3Downed&amp;sref=https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/news/avatar-2-way-of-water-budget-b2235587.html"><em>《GQ》</em></a>杂志，他 2009 年的大片——有史以来最成功的电影——的续集成本如此之高，以至于他告诉《GQ》它代表了“电影史上最糟糕的商业案例”。</p><p>卡梅隆声称，为了让续集简单地实现收支平衡，它必须成为“历史上第三或第四高票房的电影”。</p><p> “这就是你的门槛，”他说。 “这就是你的收支平衡。”</p><p>尽管如此，它并不是历史上最昂贵的电影。为此，请往下看那些制作成本更高的电影。 </p><figure id="attachment_3341169" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3341169" style="width: 1814px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3341169" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Screenshot-2022-11-02-at-13.31.50.jpg" alt="阿凡达" width="1814" height="956" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Screenshot-2022-11-02-at-13.31.50.jpg 1814w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Screenshot-2022-11-02-at-13.31.50-400x211.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Screenshot-2022-11-02-at-13.31.50-800x422.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Screenshot-2022-11-02-at-13.31.50-696x367.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Screenshot-2022-11-02-at-13.31.50-1392x734.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Screenshot-2022-11-02-at-13.31.50-1068x563.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 1814px) 100vw, 1814px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3341169" class="wp-caption-text"> 《阿凡达：水之道》。图片来源：20 世纪工作室</figcaption></figure><h3><strong>有史以来制作成本最高的电影是哪部？</strong></h3><p>无论是否考虑通货膨胀因素，2015 年的<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/reviews-various-artists-16360-308365"><em>《星球大战：原力觉醒》都</em></a>被认为是有史以来最昂贵的电影，J·J·艾布拉姆斯的星球大战续集三部曲中的第一部电影耗资高达 4.47 亿美元（3.63 亿英镑）。</p><p>排在其后的是 2018 年的<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/jurassic-world-film-review-2333571-2333571"><em>《侏罗纪世界：堕落王国</em></a>》，花费 4.32 亿美元（3.51 亿英镑），而排名前 10 的其他电影包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/star-wars-the-rise-of-skywalker-review-2588839"><em>《星球大战：天行者崛起》</em></a> （3.38 亿英镑）、 <em>《加勒比海盗：惊涛怪浪》（</em> 3.38 亿英镑） 3.08 亿英镑）和<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/reviews-various-artists-16045-316000"><em>《复仇者联盟：奥创纪元</em></a>》（2.97 亿英镑）。</p><p>第一部<em>《阿凡达》</em>电影目前以 29 亿美元（24 亿英镑）的票房收入成为有史以来票房最高的电影。 <em>《复仇者联盟：终局之战》</em>以 27.9 亿美元（24.5 亿英镑）排名第二， <em>《泰坦尼克号》</em>以 22 亿美元（21.9 亿英镑）排名第三。</p><p>有史以来票房收入排名第四和第五的电影是<em>《原力觉醒</em>》和<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/avengers-infinity-war-film-review-2301891"><em>《复仇者联盟：无限战争》</em></a> ，票房收入分别为 20.5 亿美元（17.2 亿英镑）和 20.4 亿美元（17 亿英镑）。</p><p>帖子<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/what-is-the-most-expensive-movie-ever-made-3532938">有史以来最昂贵的电影是什么？</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
